                            <rs key="#Muslims">Sarracenis</rs> fuerat. Cuius habitatores, qui
                        evadere potuerunt, <placeName key="#Churches" ref="#places/110"
                            >Beneventum</placeName> venerunt et a principibus ac civibus auxilium
                        postulantes <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/1991">Sancte Crucis</orgName> in honore <rs
                            key="#Churches">ecclesiam</rs> constructam acceperunt, ubi aliquandiu
                        habitantes, <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/1990">Victorini martiris</orgName> <rs
